Billing

Never accept raw cc number
Never store cc numbers
Always use outside payment processor (this app uses stripe)


*Uses Stripe to process payments. Use 4242 4242 4242 4242 and any future exp date and security code to use a test dummy card

Node

*Uses SendGrid as mailer

*Uses MongoDB (mlab) for backend, mongoose for model management

*Hosted on Heroku

Various NPM packages and technologies used:
  create-react-app
  mongoose schema
  Auth: cookie-session, passport, google strategy

React Frontend:
  Redux cycle,
  React Router
